{
  "texts": [
    "By analyzing a new employee's initial responses and role, AI can tailor content to be both relevant and engaging through interactive tutorials and simulations, which can ease integration into the organization, particularly for roles requiring hands-on learning and experience.",
    "Another advantage of knowledge transfer is the instantaneous nature of AI.",
    "Users can receive immediate answers to their questions, a boon for globally distributed teams where time zones can delay communication.",
    "GenAI can also reduce communication barriers in knowledge transfer because employees may be less inhibited when asking GenAI questions versus a supervisor or coworkers.",
    "This ensures that consistent and accurate information is transferred and communicated."
  ]
}